---
---
<div class="atmo"></div>
<div class="atmo-2"></div>

<div class="hero-strip reveal">
  <div class="live-badge">
    <div class="live-dot"></div>
    14 Vagas Abertas · Turma 2026
  </div>

  <h1 class="headline">
    O goleiro já escolheu ser diferente.<br />
    <em>A partir de agora, o seu treino também precisa ser.</em>
  </h1>

  <p class="subheadline">
    <strong>+1.200 goleiros já treinaram com o Método Goleiro 2.0.</strong> Musculação desenvolvida especificamente para goleiros de todos os níveis e idades. Força e explosão para se tornar um paredão nos jogos e peladas. Responda 4 perguntas e veja se você tem o perfil para a próxima turma.
  </p>

  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="stat-n">73K</span>
      <span class="stat-l">Seguidores</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="stat-n">+1.2K</span>
      <span class="stat-l">Goleiros treinados</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <span class="stat-n">100%</span>
      <span class="stat-l">Online</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .atmo {
    position: fixed; top: -30vh; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 140vw; height: 80vh;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(223,255,0,.09) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }
  .atmo-2 {
    position: fixed; bottom: -20vh; right: -20vw;
    width: 80vw; height: 80vh;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(223,255,0,.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-strip {
    width: 100%; max-width: 680px;
    padding: 56px 0 48px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }

  .live-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--neon);
    background: var(--neon-dim);
    border: 1px solid rgba(223,255,0,.2); border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 5px 14px; margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .live-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--neon);
    animation: blink 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .headline {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 6.5vw, 3.8rem);
    line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: .01em;
    text-align: center; color: var(--white); text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .headline em {
    font-style: normal; color: var(--neon); display: block;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(223,255,0,.4), 0 0 120px rgba(223,255,0,.15);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .slash {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 12vw, 6.5rem);
    color: var(--muted); line-height: .95; display: block; text-align: center;
  }

  .subheadline {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.2rem); font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;
    max-width: 520px; letter-spacing: .01em;
  }
  .subheadline strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; }

  .stats-bar {
    margin-top: 32px; width: 100%;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden; background: var(--card);
  }
  .stat-cell {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 8px; gap: 3px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border); position: relative;
  }
  .stat-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-cell::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px; background: var(--neon); opacity: 0; transition: opacity .3s;
  }
  .stat-cell:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .stat-n {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--neon); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: .02em;
  }
  .stat-l {
    font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; text-align: center;
  }
</style>
